      <title>中国在抛售股票后冻结量化基金账户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-freezes-accounts-of-quant-fund-after-it-dumped-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，一家大型量化对冲基金在一分钟内抛售了 25.7 亿元人民币（约合 3.6 亿美元）的股票，中国两家主要证券交易所将该基金的账户冻结了三天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-freezes-accounts-of-quant-fund-after-it-dumped-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 12:43:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
